      "introTitle": "Intro 1: What Is a Rational Number?",
      "introQuestion": "Have you ever shared a pizza and wondered how to write your share as a number?",
      "introExplanation": "Rational numbers are numbers that can be written as a fraction, like p/q, where p and q are whole numbers and q is not zero. They help us express parts of a whole, like slices of pizza or pieces of chocolate, making counting more flexible.",
